title: LINCS Pilot Phase Joint Project
description: The dose-dependent sensitivities of 6 nonmalignant breast and breast cancer cell lines were assayed by the HMS LINCS Center by measuring cell counts 72 hours after treatment with each of 107 small molecule inhibitors across a 6-point dose range. For further information about the assay and to download this dataset \([#20252](http://lincs.hms.harvard.edu/db/datasets/20252/)) or the cell count datasets from which the metrics were calculated \([#20245 to #20251](http://lincs.hms.harvard.edu/db/datasets/)), please visit the HMS LINCS Database.
